Env.Page.Title = Prefix Announcement SLAAC

Env.Help.Text <<EOM
IPv6-compatible devices get their IP address via an auto-configuration system named <b>SLAAC</b> (Stateless Address Auto-configuration).
<br /><br />You can active or deactivate this mechanism. However, deactivating it will cause the loss of IPv6 connectivity on your devices that only support the IPv6 adressing system.
EOM

Env.Var.dhcp_slaac.Header = Prefix Announcement (<abbr title="Stateless address autoconfiguration">SLAAC</abbr>)

Env.Text.slaac_off_warning = Warning: if you change some settings, you may cause a loss of service of your IPV6-connected devices; this section is for expert users.